{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_011EkSQFFjV6bhqSKepcrEAq","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a complete understanding of the codebase. Let me write the new test file with all the missing test coverage. I'll add tests to the existing test file.\n\nLet me plan the tests:\n\n**Curator corruption scenarios:**\n1. LLM returns conversational meta-text without code fences\n2. LLM returns response shorter than original (content loss)\n3. LLM returns empty string\n4. LLM returns only code fences with no content\n5. Multiple rapid Apply() calls (race condition) - use sync.WaitGroup\n\n**Orchestrator:**\n1. Reflector produces duplicate lessons already in knowledge base\n\n\n2. handleNewStep adds step that already exists\n3. Workflow valid after N evolution cycles\n4. Errors in one lesson don't prevent others (continue behavior)\n\n**Collector:**\n1. Test with actual store mocks\n2. Test ListRunsSince called with correct since run ID\n\n**Integration:**\n1. Corrupt prompt → evolution → detected and fixed\n2. Stability: N cycles on stable workflow → no drift\n\nNow I'll write these tests and add them to the existing test file.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2595,"cache_read_input_tokens":40037,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2595},"output_tokens":9,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d40c3d83-4916-4139-bbf3-80547b0a564f","uuid":"5556b22a-0a44-427d-af74-0e2329f8446f"}
